('Saturday afternoon ukulele meetup!', 5, 5, 'Lets get together (virtually) and strum some ukuleles!This meetup is in strum-along format. Audio latency (the time it takes sound to go from one persons microphone through the Internet to the next persons headphones) makes traditional strum-alongs impossible, but we are adapting.', 'https://c.tadst.com/gfx/1200x675/sunrise.png?1', '2021-09-13');
